  "3156430": {
    "name": "Storm of spring",
    "steam_appid": 3156430,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Synopsis</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Draw the wind and let the fluffy jellyfish fly!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Go to the right place to sprout and put down roots, to a well-sunlit area.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gameplay</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use only the mouse. Let the wind blow and let the fluffy jellyfish fly high!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game is a so-called Foddian type &quot;climbing&quot; game. Climb, fall, and climb again.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Two difficulty levels and two endings.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Easy Mode</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you are not good at climbing games, don't worry!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can retry as many times as you want from a checkpoint.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >However, there are some areas and endings that cannot be reached.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Hard Mode</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Normal game. Checkpoints are just decorations.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Scenery</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Don't get fed up with the ever-changing road, the game changes from day to night.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >At night it is dark and hard to see the terrain? If that's the case, you can fix the time in the options.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Video Streaming</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >For live streaming and video submissions using this game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Individuals, corporations, with or without revenue are allowed.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If possible, please include the title of the game and a link to the Steam store page.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >For bug reports</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Please post to the Discussion.</p>",
